Webmail:
  Send Email (using template or not)
  Save sent emails
  Edit and resend
  Delete Sent email

Webmail: 
[from email], [from name], 
[to emails ","], [cc emails ","], [bcc emails ","]
[subject]
[content]
[attachments]

state (send or not send, draft) [Save or Send(By sending email , email will be saved also]

(attachements save as binary database + extention)

Webmail_Email_Model
id, from_name, from_email, to_emails, 
cc_emails, bcc_emails, subject, content, 
state(draft, send, faild)
createat, sendat

webmail_mail_has_crm_account [webmail_mail_id, crm_account_id]

mail_attachement [id, mail_id, binary, ext]

example: 
 Account Registration  -> send mail

